<p>The writing&#8217;s fine. The only moving story I&#8217;ve appreciated in ages. Great stuff Aaron.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by <a rel="nofollow" href="http://dannyayers.com">Danny Ayers</a>
 on August 27, 2008 <a href="#c1" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
