<p>Great story.  I remember WWW2002 fondly too, mostly for Kevin Hughes&#8217; party at his place in the mountains behind - and overlooking - Honolulu (TimBL was there too).  I also remember going out to dinner with you, Rohit Khare, and Roy Fielding, and you eating only rice there too.  Shame we didn&#8217;t take any pictures.  Good times.</p>

